{"lastModified":1763637903024,"uri":"c::18263540498::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe Sun Odyssey 440, a brand-new model for 2023, is the perfect blend of elegance, innovation, and performance. This cutting-edge sailboat features a spacious four-cabin version that comfortably accommodates up to 10 people, with two additional spaces in the saloon. Ideal for both short trips and long-distance adventures, the Sun Odyssey 440 comes equipped with a bow thruster, perfect for smooth and easy manoeuvres, even in challenging conditions.\n\nDesigned with the modern sailor in mind, the boat also includes solar panels, an inverter, and air conditioning for enhanced comfort on long journeys. The new-generation Sun Odyssey line reflects harmony and well-being on board, with an ergonomic layout that facilitates ease of movement. The interior is both luxurious and functional, creating a welcoming, warm ambiance that makes every sailing experience special.\n\nWhether you’re navigating the open seas or enjoying a relaxing cruise, the Sun Odyssey 440 offers unmatched comfort, style, and performance. Ideal for those seeking a luxurious and efficient sailing experience, this yacht brings beauty and practicality together seamlessly.","blueprint":{"name":"NORTHWIND 44","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458::assets::867cada0-8cc1-11f0-98e1-39f550b59bb0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458::assets::867ea970-8cc1-11f0-98e1-39f550b59bb0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458::assets::867bea50-8cc1-11f0-98e1-39f550b59bb0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458::assets::867c1160-8cc1-11f0-98e1-39f550b59bb0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::4fb04750-8c8f-11f0-9b90-675846daa458::assets::86816890-8cc1-11f0-98e1-39f550b59b